Greece’s Opap to Start Operating New Games at Selected Locations

-- B y   T o m   S t o u k a s
-- 
2011-03-17T07:55:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/greece-s-opap-to-start-operating-new-games-at-selected-locations.html
  Opap SA (OPAP) ,  Europe ’s biggest listed
gambling company, will start four new monitor games on March 22
for a trial period in Thessaloniki,  Greece ’s second-largest
city, and two other provincial towns, according to an e-mailed
statement from the company.  OPAP GA <Equity> CN  To contact the reporter on this story:
